import React from 'react'
import { createStore, applyMiddleware } from 'redux'
import { render } from 'react-dom'
import { Provider } from 'react-redux'
import { composeWithDevTools } from 'redux-devtools-extension';
import thunk from 'redux-thunk'
import reducers from './reducers'
import Dashboard from './components/Dashboard'
import ajaxMiddleware from './reducers/ajaxMiddleware'
import styles from './styles/app.css'

let store = createStore(
	reducers, 
	composeWithDevTools(
		applyMiddleware(
			ajaxMiddleware, 
			thunk
		)
	)
)

render(
	<Provider store={ store }>
		<Dashboard />
	</Provider>,
	document.getElementById('container')
)

import { combineReducers } from 'redux'
import reports from './reports'
import graphs from './graphs'
import graphTypes from './graphTypes'
import mode from './mode'
import selectedGraph from './selectedGraph'
import session from './session'

const reducers = combineReducers({
	reports,
	graphs,
	graphTypes,
	mode,
	selectedGraph,
	session
})

export default reducers

import Alert from 'react-s-alert'
import * as CONSTANTS from '../constants'


const mode = (state = CONSTANTS.LOAD_GRAPHS, action) => {
	switch (action.type) {
		case CONSTANTS.RETRIEVE_REPORT_DATA:
			return CONSTANTS.LOADING
		case CONSTANTS.RETRIEVE_REPORT_METADATA:
			return CONSTANTS.LOADING
		case CONSTANTS.RETRIEVE_REPORT_DATA:
			return CONSTANTS.LOADING


		case CONSTANTS.DELETE_GRAPH_ERROR:
			Alert.error('Error Deleting Graph', {
	            position : 'top-right',
	            effect   : 'scale',
	            beep     : false,
	            timeout  : 5000,
	            offset   : 0
        	})

			return CONSTANTS.LOADING
		case CONSTANTS.UPDATE_GRAPH_ERROR:
			Alert.error('Error Updating Graph', {
	            position : 'top-right',
	            effect   : 'scale',
	            beep     : false,
	            timeout  : 5000,
	            offset   : 0
        	})

			return CONSTANTS.LOADING
		case CONSTANTS.REFRESH_GRAPH_ERROR:
			Alert.error('Error Refresing Graph', {
	            position : 'top-right',
	            effect   : 'scale',
	            beep     : false,
	            timeout  : 5000,
	            offset   : 0
        	})

			return CONSTANTS.LOADING
		case CONSTANTS.RETRIEVE_REPORT_DATA_ERROR:
			Alert.error('Error Retrieving Report Data', {
	            position : 'top-right',
	            effect   : 'scale',
	            beep     : false,
	            timeout  : 5000,
	            offset   : 0
        	})

			return CONSTANTS.LOADING


		case CONSTANTS.RETRIEVE_REPORT_DATA_COMPLETE:
			return CONSTANTS.READY
		case CONSTANTS.RETRIEVE_REPORT_METADATA_COMPLETE:
			return CONSTANTS.READY
		case CONSTANTS.REFRESH_GRAPH_COMPLETE:
			Alert.success('Graph Refreshed Successfully', {
	            position : 'top-right',
	            effect   : 'scale',
	            beep     : false,
	            timeout  : 5000,
	            offset   : 0
        	})

			return CONSTANTS.READY
		case CONSTANTS.LOAD_GRAPHS_COMPLETE:
			return CONSTANTS.READY


		case CONSTANTS.NEW_GRAPH:
			return CONSTANTS.NEW


		case CONSTANTS.EDIT_GRAPH:
			return CONSTANTS.EDIT


		case CONSTANTS.DELETE_GRAPH:
			Alert.success('Graph Successfully Deleted', {
	            position : 'top-right',
	            effect   : 'scale',
	            beep     : false,
	            timeout  : 5000,
	            offset   : 0
        	})

			return CONSTANTS.DELETE


		case CONSTANTS.CANCEL_EDITING:
			return CONSTANTS.VIEW
		case CONSTANTS.UPDATE_GRAPH_COMPLETE:
			Alert.success('Graph Successfully Updated', {
	            position : 'top-right',
	            effect   : 'scale',
	            beep     : false,
	            timeout  : 5000,
	            offset   : 0
        	})

			return CONSTANTS.VIEW
		case CONSTANTS.CREATE_GRAPH_COMPLETE:
			Alert.success('Graph Successfully Created', {
	            position : 'top-right',
	            effect   : 'scale',
	            beep     : false,
	            timeout  : 5000,
	            offset   : 0
        	})

			return CONSTANTS.VIEW
		default:
			return state
	}
}

export default mode
